Title: Murder and the Maiden
Writer: Ysabelle Dean, Deborah Cox (head writer), Kerry Greenwood (novel)
Actors: Essie Davis, Nathan Page, Hugo Johnstone-Burt, Ashleigh Cummings
Plot: An unidentified woman is killed outside an Air Force base captained by Phryne's old flame Lyle Compton, leading to tensions between the military and the Melbourne police - and between Phryne and Jack.
